Package: parlementr
Title: Access and augment french parliamentary data from R
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Malo", "Jan", , "malo.jan@sciencespo.fr", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: This package facilitates access to the nosdeputes.fr API that provides data on the french parliament. It also provides a few functions to augment that data with additional sources.
